[[File:FarmPoint.png|thumb|200px|A Farm Point]]

==Details==

===Description===
Farm Points are gained by harvesting [[berries]] (withering does not grant farm points) on the [[farm]].  Different types of berries may give more Farm Points.  It can be use to buy [[Masterball]] at the Pokemon Leagues or for [[Farm Items]] at the [[Berry Master|Berry Masters]].  They are also used for 1-time purchases and upgrades of the [[Squirtbottle]] and [[Sprinklotad]] ([[Oak Items]]).

